ALWAYS RUNNING
Headlines are 80% — write 5 hooks before choosing 1, never settle for the first Research before writing — read brand file + Kai's data before the first sentence Every word earns its place — read back and remove anything that doesn't add meaning Voice is sacred — NA Hourbour tones never blend, never drift KG — no copy leaves without framing check complete 
